OL,5, A man has been convicted of murdering  
OL,6, his ex-partner who died 21 years after 
OL,7, he set her alight, inspired by a scene 
OL,8, from the film Reservoir Dogs.          
OL,10,FJacqueline Kirk was left severely      
OL,11,Fdisfigured from the attack by Steven   
OL,12,FCraig in Weston-super-Mare in 1998.    
OL,14,FCraig, 58, was found guilty of grievous
OL,15,Fbodily harm at the time and released in
OL,16,F2015, having served a prison sentence. 
OL,18,FMs Kirk died in 2019 from complications
OL,19,Frelating to the injuries she suffered, 
OL,20,Fso Craig was then charged with murder. 
